==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Colorist
<hw>Col"or*ist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>coloriste</ets>.]</ety> <def>One who colors; an artist who excels
in the use of colors; one to whom coloring is of prime
importance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Titian, Paul Veronese, Van Dyck, and the rest of the good
<qex>colorists</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Colorless</ent>⟦br⟧
